JVLens is not an official HuatuoGPT-Vision repository or release.

HuatuoGPT-Vision model weights, tokenizer files, processor files, and support code are external upstream assets. Users are responsible for obtaining them lawfully and complying with the upstream license, model card, acceptable-use terms, and citation requirements.

This staging package does not include HuatuoGPT-Vision model weights, tokenizer files, processor files, support code, local cache snapshots, private datasets, or real dataset images.

This staging package includes the layer16 n50 fitted JLens matrix for review and release preparation. See weights/README.md for the matrix contract, checksum, and metadata notes.
